1. *Šešir* mu je pao na zemlju. (His hat fell to the ground.) 
2. On je nosio *šešir*. (He was wearing a hat.)
3. Dete je imalo *šešir* na glavi. (The child had a hat on his head.)
4. On je spustio *šešir*. (He took off his hat.)
5. Nosi *šešir* svaki put kada izlazi. (He wears a hat every time he goes out.)
6. Ona je često nosila *šešir*. (She often wore a hat.)
7. On je prekrstio ruke ispod *šešira*. (He crossed his arms under his hat.)